sentences.sContent: For most of the year, the area is teeming with tourists.
sentences.sCn: 一年的大部分时间里这个地方都挤满了游客。

remMethod.val: 和team(n. 群， 队)一起记

trans.tranCn: 倾泻； 充满， 遍布
trans.tranOther: If you say that a place is teeming with people or animals, you mean that it is crowded and the people and animals are moving around a lot
